node.text: So I decided to give a sneak peek into some unchartered areas of my life. I really feel like there are some ups and downs that I go through as a woman and as a business owner that isn’t often showcased on Instagram. Here’s a glimpse of that.  It will be very different from what you guys have already seen from me in the world of reality TV and very different from the programming that you have seen from @thezeusnetwork in the past as well. We came together collaboratively to bring you some thing a little different and I hope you guys enjoy it as much as I enjoyed sharing it with you. Premiering Sept 12th .. and if you wanted to pre-subscribe feel free to click the link in my bio ♥️
